sequenceDiagram
    participant B as Navigateur
    participant A as Astro SSG
    participant R2 as Cloudflare R2
    participant CF as Image Resizing
    participant VUE as Vue island Galerie

    B->>A: GET /album-slug
    Note over A: Page pré-rendue au build
    A->>R2: Fetch albums/album-slug.json
    R2-->>A: Métadonnées + URLs photos
    A-->>B: HTML statique + data inlinée
    B->>VUE: Hydratation island
    VUE->>VUE: justified-layout — calcul positions
    loop Chargement miniatures
        VUE->>CF: GET /cdn-cgi/image/width=400,format=webp/photo.jpg
        CF-->>VUE: WebP miniature
    end
    Note over VUE: ResizeObserver — recalcul si largeur change
